code: import pandas as pd import numpy as np from scipy.stats import entropy from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler import torch from torch import nn from torch.utils.data import DataLoader, Dataset from sklearn.metrics import roc_auc_score def calculate_entropy(s): counts = [s.count(c) for c in set(s)] prob = np.array(counts) / len(s) return entropy(prob) # Load data train = pd.read_csv("input/train.csv") test = pd.read_csv("input/test.csv") # Split f_27 into character features for i in range(10): train[f"f27_{i}"] = train["f_27"].str[i] test[f"f27_{i}"] = test["f_27"].str[i] # Add new engineered features for df in [train, test]: for letter in "ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ": df[f"f27_count_{letter}"] = df["f_27"].str.count(letter) df["f27_unique_count"] = df["f_27"].apply(lambda s: len(set(s))) df["f27_max_count"] = df["f_27"].apply(lambda s: max([s.count(c) for c in s])) df["f27_entropy"] = df["f_27"].apply(calculate_entropy) # Define features categorical = ( [f"f_{i:02d}" for i in range(7, 19)] + ["f_29", "f_30"] + [f"f27_{i}" for i in range(10)] ) numerical = ( [f"f_{i:02d}" for i in range(7)] + [f"f_{i}" for i in range(19, 27)] + ["f_28"] + [f"f27_count_{letter}" for letter in "ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ"] + ["f27_unique_count", "f27_max_count", "f27_entropy"] ) # Process categorical features for col in categorical: train_vals = train[col].unique() mapping = {v: i + 1 for i, v in enumerate(train_vals)} train[col] = train[col].map(mapping).fillna(0).astype(int) test[col] = test[col].map(mapping).fillna(0).astype(int) # Process numerical features scaler = StandardScaler() train[numerical] = scaler.fit_transform(train[numerical]) test[numerical] = scaler.transform(test[numerical]) # Split data X = train.drop(["id", "target", "f_27"], axis=1) y = train["target"] X_train, X_val, y_train, y_val = train_test_split( X, y, test_size=0.2, stratify=y, random_state=42 ) class TabDataset(Dataset): def __init__(self, cat, num, y=None): self.cat = torch.tensor(cat.values, dtype=torch.long) self.num = torch.tensor(num.values, dtype=torch.float) self.y = torch.tensor(y.values, dtype=torch.float) if y is not None else None def __len__(self): return len(self.cat) def __getitem__(self, idx): if self.y is not None: return self.cat[idx], self.num[idx], self.y[idx] return self.cat[idx], self.num[idx] train_set = TabDataset(X_train[categorical], X_train[numerical], y_train) val_set = TabDataset(X_val[categorical], X_val[numerical], y_val) class NeuralNet(nn.Module): def __init__(self, emb_sizes, num_size): super().__init__() self.embs = nn.ModuleList([nn.Embedding(n, 4) for n, _ in emb_sizes]) self.num_norm = nn.BatchNorm1d(num_size) self.layers = nn.Sequential( nn.Linear(sum(4 for _ in emb_sizes) + num_size + 1, 512), nn.BatchNorm1d(512), nn.ReLU(), nn.Dropout(0.3), nn.Linear(512, 256), nn.ReLU(), nn.Dropout(0.2), nn.Linear(256, 1), ) def forward(self, cat, num): num = self.num_norm(num) embeddings = [e(cat[:, i]) for i, e in enumerate(self.embs)] stacked = torch.stack(embeddings, dim=1) # Factorization Machine component sum_emb = torch.sum(stacked, dim=1) sum_square = torch.sum(sum_emb**2, dim=1) square_sum = torch.sum(stacked**2, dim=(1, 2)) fm_term = 0.5 * (sum_square - square_sum).unsqueeze(1) x = torch.cat( [emb.flatten(start_dim=1) for emb in embeddings] + [num, fm_term], dim=1 ) return self.layers(x) emb_sizes = [(train[c].max() + 1, 4) for c in categorical] model = NeuralNet(emb_sizes, len(numerical)).cuda() optimizer = torch.optim.Adam(model.parameters(), lr=0.001) criterion = nn.BCEWithLogitsLoss() train_loader = DataLoader(train_set, batch_size=2048, shuffle=True, num_workers=4) val_loader = DataLoader(val_set, batch_size=4096, num_workers=4) best_auc, patience = 0, 5 for epoch in range(30): model.train() for cat, num, y in train_loader: cat, num, y = cat.cuda(), num.cuda(), y.cuda() optimizer.zero_grad() loss = criterion(model(cat, num).squeeze(), y) loss.backward() optimizer.step() model.eval() preds, truths = [], [] with torch.no_grad(): for cat, num, y in val_loader: p = torch.sigmoid(model(cat.cuda(), num.cuda()).squeeze()).cpu() preds.append(p.numpy()) truths.append(y.numpy()) auc = roc_auc_score(np.concatenate(truths), np.concatenate(preds)) print(f"Epoch {epoch+1}: AUC {auc:.5f}") if auc > best_auc: best_auc = auc torch.save(model.state_dict(), "best.pt") patience = 5 else: patience -= 1 if patience == 0: break # Generate predictions model.load_state_dict(torch.load("best.pt")) test_set = TabDataset(test[categorical], test[numerical]) test_loader = DataLoader(test_set, batch_size=4096, num_workers=4) model.eval() preds = [] with torch.no_grad(): for cat, num in test_loader: p = torch.sigmoid(model(cat.cuda(), num.cuda()).squeeze()).cpu() preds.append(p.numpy()) pd.DataFrame({"id": test.id, "target": np.concatenate(preds)}).to_csv( "submission/submission.csv", index=False ) print(f"Final Validation AUC: {best_auc:.5f}")
